{
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-0r.ancient": "一位要带走我灵魂的死神？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-0r.next": "抱怨",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-1r.char": "我不是来杀你的，但你杀的人也太多了吧！你给我增加了很大的工作负担！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-2r.ancient": "你只在乎自己的工作量？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-0r.ancient": "你的工作完成了吗？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-0r.next": "抱怨",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-1r.char": "这附近的灵魂多到根本做不完好吗！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-2r.char": "你能不能至少借我几艘船？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-2r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-3r.ancient": "不能。即刻退下。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-0r.ancient": "又在偷懒？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-0r.next": "抱怨",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-1r.char": "我才没有偷懒！首先，死者灵魂的问题根本就是你造成的。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-2r.ancient": "不过是个借口。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-0r.ancient": "偷懒大王又来了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-0r.next": "抱怨",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-1r.char": "什么鬼？难道我背后有某位[red]巫女[/red]？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-1r.next": "说教",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-2r.char": "不论如何，你的实验与我无关。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-2r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-3r.char": "但是你的待人方式，尤其是对待自己造物的方式，还需要好好改进。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-3r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-4r.char": "你一直遭遇“不速之客”？那是因为你唯一的解决办法就是杀了他们，甚至不愿简单地问一句他们爬塔的原因。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-4r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-5r.char": "若任由其发展，不仅你的恶业会不断累积，别人对你的怨恨也会与日俱增。那样做是不会有好结果的。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-5r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-6r.ancient": "说完了？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-6r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-7r.char": "啊。我居然变得和四季大人一样了……",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-7r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-8r.ancient": "很遗憾，我没时间听一个懒惰死神的说教了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-attack": "Both"
}